# Diagnostics Test File
# This file demonstrates all diagnostic features of the REST Client extension

### Test 1: Valid request (should have no diagnostics)
GET https://api.example.com/users
Content-Type: application/json

### Test 2: Invalid HTTP method (should show error)
INVALID https://api.example.com/users

### Test 3: Missing URL (should show error)
GET

### Test 4: URL without scheme (should show warning)
GET api.example.com/users

### Test 5: URL with spaces (should show error)
GET https://api.example.com/users with spaces

### Test 6: Undefined variable (should show warning)
GET https://api.example.com/{{undefinedVariable}}/data

### Test 7: System variable (should be OK, no warning)
GET https://api.example.com/{{$guid}}

### Test 8: Empty variable name (should show error)
GET https://api.example.com/{{}}

### Test 9: Unclosed variable braces (should show error)
GET https://api.example.com/{{unclosed

### Test 10: Header typo - Conten-Type (should show warning)
POST https://api.example.com/users
Conten-Type: application/json

### Test 11: Header typo - contenttype (should show warning)
POST https://api.example.com/users
contenttype: application/json

### Test 12: Header with spaces in name (should show error)
GET https://api.example.com/users
My Header: value

### Test 13: Invalid header format (should show error)
GET https://api.example.com/users
InvalidHeaderNoColon

### Test 14: Valid JSON body (should be OK)
POST https://api.example.com/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "age": 30
}

### Test 15: Invalid JSON body (should show error)
POST https://api.example.com/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe"
  "email": "john@example.com"
}

### Test 16: POST without Content-Type header (should show warning)
POST https://api.example.com/users

{"name": "test"}

### Test 17: PUT without Content-Type header (should show warning)
PUT https://api.example.com/users/1

{"name": "updated"}

### Test 18: GET request (no Content-Type needed, no warning)
GET https://api.example.com/users

### Test 19: Multiple issues in one request
INVALID api.example.com/{{undefined}}/users
Conten-Type: application/json
content-length: 100

{invalid json}

### Test 20: Valid complex request
POST https://api.example.com/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{$guid}}
Accept: application/json

{
  "user": {
    "name": "Alice",
    "email": "alice@example.com",
    "preferences": {
      "theme": "dark",
      "notifications": true
    }
  }
}

### Test 21: PATCH without Content-Type (should show warning)
PATCH https://api.example.com/users/1

{"status": "active"}

### Test 22: Common header typos
GET https://api.example.com/data
authorisation: Bearer token
user-agent: MyApp
cache-control: no-cache
